Worth the download for me but I would not pay for it.  It is a very old movie, set in the 80's I'm guessing.  The garage door entry technique shown is with the old one solid panel garage door instead of the commonplace four panels seen everywhere in the United States (which gives you a sense of how old this movie is).  It is good for the novice to get ideas about the different methods of entry outside of just picking locks.  The end of the movie shows some very basic safe cracking and how to locate drill points.  I would only recommend this to novices.  Not worth a locksmith's time.
Thanks to the uploader.
